name: SonicEdge's Akeno Himejima
description:
My second Embedding.

This is a Textual Inversion of Akeno Himejima (highschool dxd). I had some trouble with this and if I'm going to be honest I still get issues with some gens, but it's fine more often than not.
Trained on 84 samples with 5000 steps.
Works for both NSFW and SFW, and has more leeway for positions than my Rias embedding, likely due to less sample images.

Works best with hires fix and some prompts such as masterpiece, 2k and a negative prompt embedding ect.

I have plans to create these as embeddings:

- Kuoh Acadamy uniform (done, uploading next)
- Rias embedding with her uniform (Not doing this, decided to just make the uniform separate and leave it at that.)
- Other DxD characters (Irina and Xenovia planned next in the series of DxD characters)
- Specific poses
- Certain fetishes
- More interesting positions

I would love to see the stuff you can generate with Akeno.

Additional notes: All examples were made using Corneos 7th heaven model (Corneo's 7th Heaven Mix | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai)
And NAIs VAE.
Prompts are:
masterpiece, highres, details, nsfw, sonicedges_akeno_himejima, Clothing, Clothing print, mood, Bodyframing, look, Angle, Pose, bg. (Bold text are wildcards)
Negative: a negative embedding called bad_prompt_version2 that I forget the source for

Sampling steps: 20
CFG Scale: 7
WxH: 384x384 with hires fix 2x upscale to 768x768

Edit: You'll likely need to use more negative prompts to fine tune the results.
